        <h2 id="mission-title" data-key="why_title">Why We Exist</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="mission-statement" data-key="why_para">Karunya Shaiji's Foundation brings hope, dignity, and meaningful support to families facing cancer. Established in 2017, the foundation has been walking alongside families through some of the hardest seasons of their lives. We believe no person should suffer in silence. Through comprehensive support in health, education, and housing, we're transforming lives across Kerala.</p>
      <p class="mission-statement" data-key="why_para_2">The vision for this foundation began with Shaiji, whose own journey with cancer opened her eyes to how alone many families feel when they are struggling. She often spoke about creating a place that would stand beside people in their hardest moments.</p>
      <p class="mission-statement" data-key="why_para_3">From that dream grew the work we carry forward today, offering practical support for cancer treatment, helping children stay in school, and building safe homes for families in need across Kerala. Her quiet courage and compassion continue to guide everything this foundation does.</p>
